short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Generates suggestions using ChatGPT for LinkedIn comments.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
** You need an OpenAI API Key to use this extension. **

This extension adds a button to LinkedIn comment boxes to fetch suggestions to reply from ChatGPT. 

You need an OpenAI Api Key to use the extension. Once you have installed this extension, you can click on the extension icon to open a small window in which you can enter the API key.
